    "# Section 5.1: Half-moons with scatter noise\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook contains the cleaned code for the half-moon experiment.  It compares\n",
    "Gamma-Dirichlet clustering with Coifman--Lafon diffusion-map clustering on the same\n",
    "fixed-bandwidth Gaussian kNN graph.\n",
    "\n",
    "All comments and figure labels in the code are written in English.\n"
   ]
